<bibRefCitation id="DC744B2AFF99FF81FDC8B143FCCAC352" author="Hempel, A." box="[628,859,1034,1060]" pageId="95" pageNumber="96" pagination="365 - 537" refId="ref78247" refString="Hempel, A. (1900) As coccidas Brazileiras. Revista do Museu Paulista. Sao Paulo, 4, 365 - 537." type="journal article" year="1900">Hempel, 1900: 375</bibRefCitation>
). The World Catalogue did not include this information in the 
<typeStatus id="675E8879FF99FF81FE85B17BFEFAC33A" box="[313,363,1074,1100]" pageId="95" pageNumber="96">type</typeStatus>
data (
<bibRefCitation id="DC744B2AFF99FF81FE0EB17BFD39C33A" author="Ben-Dov, Y." box="[434,680,1074,1100]" pageId="95" pageNumber="96" refId="ref76502" refString="Ben-Dov, Y. (2005) A Systematic Catalogue of the Scale Insect Family Margarodidae (Hemiptera: Coccoidea) of the World. Intercept Ltd., Wimborne, U. K., 400 pp." type="book" year="2005">Ben-Dov, 2005: 219</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
